a platform that provides businesses, creative professionals, and individuals with access to high-quality licensed images, illustrations, and videos. Founded in 1999, Alamy is based in the UK and has become one of the largest and most successful stock media platforms in the world.</p>\r\n<p>Alamy offers a vast library of over 215 million assets, including stock photos, illustrations, vectors, and videos, and adds over 100,000 new assets every day. The platform features a wide range of content, including exclusive content that can\'t be found on any other stock media platform.</p>\r\n<p>Alamy has a number of features and tools that make it easy for users to find and license the content they need. The platform\'s search engine allows users to search for images by keyword, category, color, and more. It also offers curated collections and featured content to help users discover new and relevant images.</p>\r\n<p>Alamy offers several pricing models for licensing content, including individual image downloads and subscription plans. Contributors to Alamy can earn a percentage of the revenue generated from their licensed content, with rates ranging from 40% to 50%.</p>\r\n<p>Overall, Alamy is a reliable and high-quality resource for businesses, creatives, and anyone in need of licensed visual content. With its vast library of assets, user-friendly features and tools, and flexible licensing options, Alamy is a great choice for anyone looking to enhance their marketing, branding, or creative projects.</p>\r\n<p><strong>official site&nbsp;</strong>https://www.alamy.com/</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Etsy</h2>\r\n<div class=\"w-full border-b border-black/10 dark:border-gray-900/50 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 group bg-gray-50 dark:bg-[#444654]\">\r\n<div class=\"text-base gap-4 md:gap-6 m-auto md:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-2xl xl:max-w-3xl p-4 md:py-6 flex lg:px-0\">\r\n<div class=\"relative flex w-[calc(100%-50px)] flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3 lg:w-[calc(100%-115px)]\">\r\n<div class=\"fl